    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.1/jquery.min.js" integrity="sha512-v2CJ7UaYy4JwqLDIrZUI/4hqeoQieOmAZNXBeQyjo21dadnwR+8ZaIJVT8EE2iyI61OV8e6M8PP2/4hpQINQ/g==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-DTOQO9RWCH3ppGqcWaEA1BIZOC6xxalwEsw9c2QQeAIftl+Vegovlnee1c9QX4TctnWMn13TZye+giMm8e2LwA==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <title>Cuban Cigars</title>
</head>

<body>

    <nav class="nav">

        <div class="cigarLogo">
            <a href="/customer/">
                <img src="/images/Cuban Cigars_transparent.png" alt="Cuban Cigars Logo">
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <ul class="navList">
            <li><a href="" class="active">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href=""><i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i></a></li>
            <li><a href="/customer/settings"><i class="fas fa-cog"></i></a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <div class="menuButton">
        <i class="fa fa-bars"></i>
    </div>

    <section class="websiteContent">
        <h1> Hello <%= name %> </h1>
        <p>Get the most authentic Cigars delivered to your door right now!</p>
        <button>Shop Here</button>
    </section>

    <h1 class="heading">Our flagship products</h1>
    
    <div class="mainContent">
        <div class="products">
            <img src="/images/Cuaba.jpg">
            <h3>Cuaba - Distinguidos</h3>
            <br>
            <p>Open wood and herbaceous aromas are easily detectable to the uninitiated palate leaving the focus on the time and rhythm of the vitola itself. I describe this cigar as “a teacher amongst the double Figurado vitola”</p>
            <h6>£400.00</h6>
            <button>Buy Now</button>
        </div>
    
        <div class="products">
            <img src="/images/Cohiba.jpg">
            <h3>Cohiba Cigars</h3>
            <br>
            <p>Renowned for their bold and robust flavor profiles, the extended fermentation process not only darkens the wrapper but also contributes to the development of complex, sweet, and sometimes spicy notes. Maduro enthusiasts often appreciate the depth and intensity that these cigars bring to the palate </p>
            <h6>£1200.00</h6>
            <button>Buy Now</button>
        </div>
    
        <div class="products">
            <img src="/images/Romeo.jpg">
            <h3>Romeo y Julieta Cigar</h3>
            <br>
            <p>Great size and decent length give these belicosos a first-class draw and a full flavour. With age, these are impressive little figurados. Medium bodied with good burning characteristics, and a cedary, often whisky tone that makes these a good afternoon smoke</p>
            <h6>£600.00</h6>
            <button>Buy Now</button>
        </div>    
    </div>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy;Copyright at <a href="/customer/">Cuban Cigars</a></p>

        
    </footer>

    <script>
        $(document).ready(function(){
            $("button").click(function() {
                $('html, body').animate({
                    scrollTop: $(".mainContent").offset().top
                }, 1000); 
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
